errors.title: Feature not enabled in the plan.
errors.detail: published_at must be after 2022-05-02T00:00:00Z, instead got [2022-01-01T00:00:00Z TO *]. This might be because your plan does not have access to data before 2022-05-02T00:00:00Z. You can read more about working with dates here: https://docs.aylien.com/newsapi/common-workflows/#working-with-dates
